sources.description:
When the fire's out...the heat is on!
Tensions arise when a previously all-white firehouse gets a new rookie, and it's first African American team member.  He must face with both physical tests and the racism of his peers as he works to become a fully fledged fire fighter. 

Original title: Firehouse (1973) 
This film is subtitled in many languages.

Director: Alex March
Writer: Frank Cucci
Stars: Richard Roundtree, Sheila Frazier, Michael Lerner, Paul Le Mat, Val Avery
Genres: Action, Drama
